public class SFEEWriter
extends AbstractWriter<Connection>
implements org.openadaptor.core.IDataProcessor

This component is responsible for writing SFEE tracker items encoded in the generic XML artifact format back to the SFEE tracker

setResyncUserName

public void setResyncUserName(java.lang.String resyncUserName)
Sets the optional resync username The resync user name is used to login into the SFEE/CSFE instance whenever an artifact should be created. This user has to differ from the ordinary user used to log in in order to force initial resyncs with the source system once a new artifact has been created.

Parameters:
resyncUserName - the resyncUserName to set
